<div id="pf25" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="25"><div class="pc pc25 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="magfile/bg25.png"/><div class="c xbf y68c w32 h186"><div class="t m0 x3d h127 y68d ff97 fsdd fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">Images from marukopum, Siberian <span class="_ _5"></span>Art, </div><div class="t m0 x3c h127 y68e ff97 fsdd fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">Thanun Patiparnthada/Shutterstock.com</div></div><div class="t m0 x98 h180 y68f ff92 fs50 fc43 sc0 ls42 ws0">Below are words with PLANT in them.</div><div class="t m0 xf8 h180 y690 ff92 fs50 fc43 sc0 ls42 ws0">Underline the right word in each sentence<span class="_ _5"></span>. Happy ‘PL<span class="_ _0"></span>ANTING<span class="_ _5"></span>’!</div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y691 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">1. Medical <span class="_ _6"></span>science <span class="_ _6"></span>has <span class="_ _6"></span>advanced by <span class="_ _6"></span>leaps <span class="_ _6"></span>and <span class="_ _6"></span>bounds. Did <span class="_ _6"></span>you <span class="_ _6"></span>know <span class="_ _6"></span>that<span class="ff2b ls0 ws0"> </span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y692 ff2b fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws0">    even skin <span class="ff59">replants / transplants<span class="ff2c ws13"> are <span class="_ _6"></span>possible?</span></span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y693 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">2. The younger <span class="_ _6"></span>brother <span class="_ _6"></span><span class="ff59 ws0">supplanted / transplanted<span class="ff2b"> his older sister and stole<span class="ls0"> </span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y694 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">  <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span>the inheritance <span class="_ _6"></span>that <span class="_ _6"></span>was <span class="_ _6"></span>due to <span class="_ _6"></span>the <span class="_ _6"></span>rst <span class="_ _6"></span>child in <span class="_ _6"></span>the <span class="_ _6"></span>family<span class="_ _4"></span>.</div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y695 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">3. Downloading <span class="_ _6"></span>software <span class="_ _6"></span>from <span class="_ _6"></span>unrecognised sources <span class="_ _6"></span>may <span class="_ _6"></span><span class="ff59 ws0">implant / displant<span class="ff2b ls0"> </span></span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y696 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">  <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span>viruses or <span class="_ _6"></span>give <span class="_ _6"></span>hackers <span class="_ _6"></span>unwarranted access <span class="_ _6"></span>to <span class="_ _6"></span>sensitive <span class="_ _6"></span>information on <span class="_ _6"></span>your<span class="ff2b ls0 ws0"> </span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y697 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">  <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span> <span class="_ _6"></span>mobile phone.</div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y698 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">4. These coconuts <span class="_ _6"></span>were <span class="_ _6"></span>harvested <span class="_ _6"></span>from his <span class="_ _6"></span>various <span class="_ _6"></span><span class="ff59 ws0">plantations / houseplants<span class="ff2b ls0">.</span></span></div><div class="t m0 xc0 hf7 y699 ff2b fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">5. <span class="ff59 ws0">Plantains / Eggplants</span><span class="ff2c"> <span class="_ _6"></span>are <span class="_ _6"></span>a <span class="_ _6"></span>type of <span class="_ _6"></span>fruit. They <span class="_ _6"></span>are <span class="_ _6"></span>also known <span class="_ _6"></span>as <span class="_ _6"></span>brinjals.</span></div><div class="c x2c y69a w33 h187"><div class="t m0 x7a h188 y69b ff98 fs11c fc3 sc0 ls45 ws4d">Lang <span class="_ _0"></span>Game</div></div><div class="c xc7 y69c w1e h137"><div class="t m0 x8b h132 y2b4 ff99 fs77 fc2 sc0 lsb ws0">Answers can be found on page 43</div></div><div class="t m0 x110 h17d y69d ff8d fsef fc43 sc0 ls3e ws5">Pick the ri<span class="_ _5"></span>g<span class="_ _5"></span>ht PLAN<span class="_ _5"></span>T!</div><div class="t m0 xf2 hf8 y1b9 ff2d fs13 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">37</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf26" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="26"><div class="pc pc26 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="magfile/bg26.png"/><div class="c x0 y0 w21 h0"><div class="t me2 x111 h189 y69e ff9a fs11d fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">?</div></div><div class="t m0 x3f h18a y69f ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Oh, you must mean these plants I have in my balcony. </div><div class="t m0 x41 h18a y6a0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Yes, I guess it can be considered a mini-farm, </div><div class="t m0 x37 h18a y6a1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">apartment style! I started this after I received the </div><div class="t m0 x41 h18a y6a2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">seed packets distributed by the government.</div><div class="t m0 x4d h18a y6a3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I did not know about </div><div class="t m0 x4e h18a y6a4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the ‘30 by 30’ goal! </div><div class="t m0 x112 h18a y6a5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">It sounds exciting </div><div class="t m0 x3f h18a y6a6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">for a small city </div><div class="t m0 x112 h18a y6a7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">state like ours to </div><div class="t m0 x36 h18a y6a8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow our own food. I </div><div class="t m0 x3e h18a y6a9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">just tried to grow </div><div class="t m0 x6 h18a y6aa ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">my own food in a </div><div class="t m0 x4e h18a y6ab ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">small way using the </div><div class="t m0 x37 h18a y6ac ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">seed packets.</div><div class="t m0 x20 h18a y6ad ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Yes, I can see you have </div><div class="t m0 x9f h18a y6ae ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">tomatoes and the leafy </div><div class="t m0 x1e h18a y6af ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">kang kong! I received lady’s </div><div class="t m0 x2a h18a y6b0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">finger and the leafy </div><div class="t m0 x113 h18a y6b1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetable cai xin seed </div><div class="t m0 x1f h18a y6b2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">packets, but I have yet to </div><div class="t m0 x1e h18a y6b3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">start growing them. I&apos;m not </div><div class="t m0 xba h18a y6b4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">very confident about doing </div><div class="t m0 xda h18a y6b5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">that, to be honest.</div><div class="t m0 x10d h18a y6b6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">The seed packets </div><div class="t m0 x10d h18a y6b7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">come with a plant </div><div class="t m0 x10d h18a y6b8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">care sheet, and it </div><div class="t m0 x6 h18a y6b9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">gives you </div><div class="t m0 xb0 h18a y6ba ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">instructions on </div><div class="t m0 x3b h18a y6bb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">how to grow and </div><div class="t m0 x4e h18a y6bc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">care for the </div><div class="t m0 x3b h18a y6bd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants. It is quite </div><div class="t m0 x3b h18a y6be ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">easy. You should </div><div class="t m0 x4e h18a y6bf ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">give it a try.</div><div class="c x0 y0 w21 h0"><div class="t m0 x114 h18a y6c0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">That’s right. I went on to </div><div class="t m0 x115 h18a y6c1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow more plants after I was </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6c2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">encouraged by my success </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6c3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">with the seed packets! The </div><div class="t m0 x114 h18a y6c4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">most important thing for </div><div class="t m0 x117 h18a y6c5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants, especially vegetable </div><div class="t m0 x114 h18a y6c6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants that bear fruit, is </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6c7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">sunlight. You need to place </div><div class="t m0 x117 h18a y6c8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the plants at a place for at </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6c9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">least eight hours of direct </div><div class="t m0 x118 h18a y6ca ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">sun every day. Leafy </div><div class="t m0 x117 h18a y6cb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables can still grow in </div><div class="t m0 x119 h18a y6cc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">less light, though.</div><div class="t m0 x11a h18a y6cd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I think I will, now that I </div><div class="t m0 x11a h18a y6ce ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">see how successful you </div><div class="t m0 x11b h18a y6cf ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">have been! I see that </div><div class="t m0 x11c h18a y6d0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">there are more plants </div><div class="t m0 x11d h18a y6d1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">here. Is that a brinjal </div><div class="t m0 x11e h18a y6d2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant and a potato </div><div class="t m0 x11d h18a y6d3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant? You must give </div><div class="t m0 x11a h18a y6d4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">me some tips on how to </div><div class="t m0 x11f h18a y6d5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow plants.</div><div class="t m0 x120 h18a y6d6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">How about the soil? </div><div class="t m0 x121 h18a y6d7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">How would I know that </div><div class="t m0 x122 h18a y6d8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the soil is rich enough </div><div class="t m0 x123 h18a y6d9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">for my plant?</div><div class="t m0 x124 h18a y6da ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">You can do a soil test. Soil test kits </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6db ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">are usually sold in the shops that sell </div><div class="t m0 x114 h18a y6dc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants. That will give you an idea of </div><div class="t m0 x125 h18a y6dd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the soil fertility and it will offer </div><div class="t m0 x126 h18a y6de ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">suggestions of what types of </div><div class="t m0 x118 h18a y6df ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">fertilisers will be best for your </div><div class="t m0 x116 h18a y6e0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant. Another thing is, keep it small. </div><div class="t m0 x118 h18a y6e1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Try planting container-friendly </div><div class="t m0 x114 h18a y6e2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables in pots or window-boxes </div><div class="t m0 x127 h18a y6e3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">on a sunny deck, for a change.</div><div class="t m0 x128 h18a y6e4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I am certainly not </div><div class="t m0 x129 h18a y6e5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">intending to have a big </div><div class="t m0 x12a h18a y6e6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">garden. Anyway, my </div><div class="t m0 x128 h18a y6e7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">small three-room </div><div class="t m0 x12b h18a y6e8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">apartment would not be </div><div class="t m0 x12b h18a y6e9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">able to accommodate it! </div><div class="t m0 x129 h18a y6ea ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Thank you for the tips, </div><div class="t m0 x129 h18a y6eb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Sue. I will go home and </div><div class="t m0 x12c h18a y6ec ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">start opening up the seed </div><div class="t m0 x12d h18a y6ed ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">packets today!</div><div class="t m0 x12e h18a y6ee ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I wish you best of luck, Dan, </div><div class="t m0 x12e h18a y6ef ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">and I hope to taste some of </div><div class="t m0 x12f h18a y6f0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">your home-grown </div><div class="t m0 x130 h18a y6f1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables soon!</div></div><div class="t m0 x81 h18a y6f2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Sue, thank you for inviting me to your </div><div class="t m0 x10c h18a y6f3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">place. Your apartment is beautiful, </div><div class="t m0 x10c h18a y6f4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">and I am particularly impressed by </div><div class="t m0 x85 h18a y6f5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">your little farm over there.</div><div class="t m0 xcf h18a y6f6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Ah yes, the ‘Gardening </div><div class="t m0 x10b h18a y6f7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">with Edibles’ programme </div><div class="t m0 x1 h18a y6f8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">that the government </div><div class="t m0 x9c h18a y6f9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">rolled out to encourage </div><div class="t m0 x9b h18a y6fa ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">home gardening. It is also </div><div class="t m0 x9c h18a y6fb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">aligned to our country’s </div><div class="t m0 x131 h18a y6fc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">‘30 by 30’ goal to produce </div><div class="t m0 xcf h18a y6fd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">30% of our nutritional </div><div class="t m0 xf3 h18a y6fe ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">needs locally by 2030.</div><div class="t m0 x8f h18b y6ff ff9c fs11f fc46 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gr<span class="_ _4"></span>owing Y<span class="_ _1c"></span>our Own Food</div><div class="t m0 x68 h18c y700 ff9c fs100 fc46 sc0 ls0 ws0">By Shoba Nair</div><div class="t m0 x12 hef y4c9 ff59 fs4d fc3 sc0 ls5 ws13">Listening</div><div class="t m0 x13 hf8 y1b9 ff2d fs13 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">38</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf27" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="27"><div class="pc pc27 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="magfile/bg27.png"/><div class="t me2 x87 h189 y69e ff9a fs11d fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">?</div><div class="c x0 y0 w21 h0"><div class="t m0 x132 h18a y69f ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Oh, you must mean these plants I have in my balcony. </div><div class="t m0 x133 h18a y6a0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Yes, I guess it can be considered a mini-farm, </div><div class="t m0 x134 h18a y6a1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">apartment style! I started this after I received the </div><div class="t m0 x133 h18a y6a2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">seed packets distributed by the government.</div><div class="t m0 x135 h18a y6a3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I did not know about </div><div class="t m0 x136 h18a y6a4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the ‘30 by 30’ goal! </div><div class="t m0 x137 h18a y6a5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">It sounds exciting </div><div class="t m0 x132 h18a y6a6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">for a small city </div><div class="t m0 x137 h18a y6a7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">state like ours to </div><div class="t m0 x135 h18a y6a8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow our own food. I </div><div class="t m0 x137 h18a y6a9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">just tried to grow </div><div class="t m0 x138 h18a y6aa ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">my own food in a </div><div class="t m0 x136 h18a y6ab ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">small way using the </div><div class="t m0 x134 h18a y6ac ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">seed packets.</div><div class="t m0 x139 h18a y6ad ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Yes, I can see you have </div><div class="t m0 x13a h18a y6ae ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">tomatoes and the leafy </div><div class="t m0 x10e h18a y6af ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">kang kong! I received lady’s </div><div class="t m0 x13b h18a y6b0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">finger and the leafy </div><div class="t m0 x13c h18a y6b1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetable cai xin seed </div><div class="t m0 xe7 h18a y6b2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">packets, but I have yet to </div><div class="t m0 x10e h18a y6b3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">start growing them. I&apos;m not </div><div class="t m0 x13d h18a y6b4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">very confident about doing </div><div class="t m0 x13e h18a y6b5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">that, to be honest.</div><div class="t m0 x13f h18a y6b6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">The seed packets </div><div class="t m0 x13f h18a y6b7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">come with a plant </div><div class="t m0 x13f h18a y6b8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">care sheet, and it </div><div class="t m0 x138 h18a y6b9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">gives you </div><div class="t m0 x140 h18a y6ba ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">instructions on </div><div class="t m0 x13f h18a y6bb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">how to grow and </div><div class="t m0 x135 h18a y6bc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">care for the </div><div class="t m0 x13f h18a y6bd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants. It is quite </div><div class="t m0 x141 h18a y6be ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">easy. You should </div><div class="t m0 x135 h18a y6bf ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">give it a try.</div></div><div class="t m0 x5b h18a y6c0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">That’s right. I went on to </div><div class="t m0 xbb h18a y6c1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow more plants after I was </div><div class="t m0 x5e h18a y6c2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">encouraged by my success </div><div class="t m0 x5e h18a y6c3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">with the seed packets! The </div><div class="t m0 x5b h18a y6c4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">most important thing for </div><div class="t m0 x142 h18a y6c5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants, especially vegetable </div><div class="t m0 x5b h18a y6c6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants that bear fruit, is </div><div class="t m0 x5e h18a y6c7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">sunlight. You need to place </div><div class="t m0 x142 h18a y6c8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the plants at a place for at </div><div class="t m0 x5e h18a y6c9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">least eight hours of direct </div><div class="t m0 xde h18a y6ca ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">sun every day. Leafy </div><div class="t m0 x142 h18a y6cb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables can still grow in </div><div class="t m0 x143 h18a y6cc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">less light, though.</div><div class="t m0 x26 h18a y6cd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I think I will, now that I </div><div class="t m0 x25 h18a y6ce ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">see how successful you </div><div class="t m0 xaa h18a y6cf ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">have been! I see that </div><div class="t m0 xd7 h18a y6d0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">there are more plants </div><div class="t m0 xaa h18a y6d1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">here. Is that a brinjal </div><div class="t m0 x144 h18a y6d2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant and a potato </div><div class="t m0 xaa h18a y6d3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant? You must give </div><div class="t m0 x25 h18a y6d4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">me some tips on how to </div><div class="t m0 x145 h18a y6d5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">grow plants.</div><div class="t m0 x89 h18a y6d6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">How about the soil? </div><div class="t m0 x88 h18a y6d7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">How would I know that </div><div class="t m0 xad h18a y6d8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the soil is rich enough </div><div class="t m0 x10b h18a y6d9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">for my plant?</div><div class="t m0 xc9 h18a y6da ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">You can do a soil test. Soil test kits </div><div class="t m0 x5e h18a y6db ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">are usually sold in the shops that sell </div><div class="t m0 x146 h18a y6dc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plants. That will give you an idea of </div><div class="t m0 xde h18a y6dd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">the soil fertility and it will offer </div><div class="t m0 x5c h18a y6de ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">suggestions of what types of </div><div class="t m0 xde h18a y6df ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">fertilisers will be best for your </div><div class="t m0 x147 h18a y6e0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">plant. Another thing is, keep it small. </div><div class="t m0 xde h18a y6e1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Try planting container-friendly </div><div class="t m0 x5b h18a y6e2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables in pots or window-boxes </div><div class="t m0 x5c h18a y6e3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">on a sunny deck, for a change.</div><div class="t m0 xc1 h18a y6e4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I am certainly not </div><div class="t m0 xe8 h18a y6e5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">intending to have a big </div><div class="t m0 xa4 h18a y6e6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">garden. Anyway, my </div><div class="t m0 xc1 h18a y6e7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">small three-room </div><div class="t m0 x1 h18a y6e8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">apartment would not be </div><div class="t m0 x148 h18a y6e9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">able to accommodate it! </div><div class="t m0 x149 h18a y6ea ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Thank you for the tips, </div><div class="t m0 xe8 h18a y6eb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Sue. I will go home and </div><div class="t m0 xf3 h18a y6ec ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">start opening up the seed </div><div class="t m0 x14a h18a y6ed ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">packets today!</div><div class="t m0 x14b h18a y6ee ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">I wish you best of luck, Dan, </div><div class="t m0 x14b h18a y6ef ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">and I hope to taste some of </div><div class="t m0 xc3 h18a y6f0 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">your home-grown </div><div class="t m0 xeb h18a y6f1 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">vegetables soon!</div><div class="c x0 y0 w21 h0"><div class="t m0 xd4 h18a y6f2 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Sue, thank you for inviting me to your </div><div class="t m0 x14c h18a y6f3 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">place. Your apartment is beautiful, </div><div class="t m0 x14c h18a y6f4 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">and I am particularly impressed by </div><div class="t m0 x14d h18a y6f5 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">your little farm over there.</div><div class="t m0 x14e h18a y6f6 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">Ah yes, the ‘Gardening </div><div class="t m0 x14f h18a y6f7 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">with Edibles’ programme </div><div class="t m0 x150 h18a y6f8 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">that the government </div><div class="t m0 x151 h18a y6f9 ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">rolled out to encourage </div><div class="t m0 x14f h18a y6fa ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">home gardening. It is also </div><div class="t m0 x152 h18a y6fb ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">aligned to our country’s </div><div class="t m0 xd5 h18a y6fc ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">‘30 by 30’ goal to produce </div><div class="t m0 x151 h18a y6fd ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">30% of our nutritional </div><div class="t m0 x14e h18a y6fe ff9b fs11e fc2 sc0 ls46 ws0">needs locally by 2030.</div></div><div class="t m0 x153 h18b y6ff ff9c fs11f fc46 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gr<span class="_ _4"></span>owing Y<span class="_ _1c"></span>our Own Food</div><div class="t m0 x6b hf1 y701 ff59 fs77 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">qrs.ly/smcp5mv</div><div class="t m0 xf2 hf8 y1b9 ff2d fs13 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">39</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
<div id="pf28" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="28"><div class="pc pc28 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="magfile/bg28.png"/><div class="t m0 xd1 h18d y702 ff9d fs120 fc47 sc0 ls0 ws0">How T<span class="_ _e"></span>o Gr<span class="_ _4"></span>ow T<span class="_ _e"></span>omatoes</div><div class="t m0 xd1 hed y703 ff2d fs4d fc47 sc0 ls5 ws0">Have you ever thought of gr<span class="_ _5"></span>owing your own tomatoes? Grow<span class="ls0">-</span></div><div class="t m0 xd1 hed y704 ff2d fs4d fc47 sc0 ls5 ws0">ing potted tomatoes on balconies, window sills or corridors<span class="_ _5"></span> </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hed y705 ff2d fs4d fc47 sc0 ls5 ws0">is becoming more common for those who live in apartments.<span class="_ _5"></span> </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hed y706 ff2d fs4d fc47 sc0 ls5 ws0">Growing tomatoes is simple and fuss-fr<span class="_ _5"></span>ee. Here ar<span class="_ _5"></span>e the steps </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hed y707 ff2d fs4d fc47 sc0 ls5 ws0">you need to take once y<span class="_ _5"></span>ou have the tomato seeds.</div><div class="t m0 xd1 hf7 y708 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">First, you’ll <span class="_ _6"></span>need <span class="_ _6"></span>one <span class="_ _6"></span>container for </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hf7 y709 ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">every two <span class="_ _6"></span>seeds. <span class="_ _6"></span>While <span class="_ _6"></span>it’s possible </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hee y70a ff2b fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws0">to raise all the seeds in the same </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hf7 y70b ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">pot, this <span class="_ _6"></span>makes <span class="_ _6"></span>the <span class="_ _6"></span>young plants </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hf7 y70c ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">harder to <span class="_ _6"></span>remove <span class="_ _6"></span>when <span class="_ _6"></span>the time </div><div class="t m0 xd1 hf7 y70d ff2c fs4d fc2 sc0 ls5 ws13">comes to <span class="_ _6"></span>transplant <span c