all stalky plant with a citrus avour<span class="_ _4"></span>.<span class="ff2b"> </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x1e h178 y909 ff59 fse1 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">C<span class="ff2c">    This spice adds colour to the food, such as curries and curry powder<span class="_ _4"></span>. <span class="ff2b"> </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x1e h178 y90a ff59 fse1 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">D<span class="ff2c">    This star-shaped spice is an integral ingredient in Chinese ve-spice powder<span class="_ _4"></span>.</span></div><div class="t m0 x1e h178 y90b ff59 fse1 fc2 sc0 ls0 ws0">E<span class="ff2c">    These are the aromatic ower buds of a tree, and are found in Indonesia.</span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
